{"tid":389132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）日本玩具廠商看準先機 推出以參考應屆香港小姐冠軍面形設計之商品","createTime":"2017-09-06T03:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T10:47:12.000Z","uid":108356,"like":1109,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a2bccc64ee5334cc534111f3087dba363f1979","tid":389132,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"據消息指日本某玩具廠商眼見香港大台TVB，日前舉行的2017香港小姐競選活動中以壓倒性的票數奪冠的雷莊兜小姐外貌姣好，尤其是下顎線條分明。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/102750_1ea8f9c7715486bc0652ec91bc6c3f82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F102750_1ea8f9c7715486bc0652ec91bc6c3f82.jpg&h=5466dbe3&s={SIZE}\" />(圖為雷莊兜小姐）<br />\n<br />\n    設計師形容：「那張小嘴巴蘊藏著她豐富的表情。高興時，撇撇嘴，扮個鬼臉、生氣時，撅起的小嘴能掙住一把小油壺。」<br />\n        <br />\n      設計師說道：「八九十年代的香港的影視劇十分蓬勃，是潮流的尖端。雖然香港影視業式微好幾十年，但我留意到最近香港冒起了一種新的審美觀 。如應屆香港小姐冠軍及香港大熱女星 蔡思達。她們都是以這種面形令香港人為之瘋狂。」<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/110658_5d6661e88808956e4bcec27a45d5b132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F110658_5d6661e88808956e4bcec27a45d5b132.jpg&h=74f5b6db&s={SIZE}\" />（圖片來源-蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n      而且由蔡斯達主演的該劇集亦大受全球歡迎。他認為這面形是來年最巨潮流及是最美的指標之一 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/103919_8ecbe3a26f2b0527599effa445be8b78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F103919_8ecbe3a26f2b0527599effa445be8b78.jpg&h=15789b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩具商以她們面容特徵設計出一系列扭蛋玩具，玩具商希望以此延續香港潮流一哥的地位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/105336_22bb8867a8b9ea490c3c50a5bdae09a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F105336_22bb8867a8b9ea490c3c50a5bdae09a6.jpg&h=530ae34b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/105350_c82f217309ef43cf666dc312c07a6b4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F105350_c82f217309ef43cf666dc312c07a6b4a.jpg&h=15677a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源-ettoday)"},{"pid":"b33472bb1cae70885eeae14ade6cdf0f3f33ea28","tid":389132,"uid":8246,"like":358,"dislike":1,"score":357,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"打咁多字,搵咁多圖,真係辛苦哂"},{"pid":"e1628dbeddf8f7c8c2a5c107e2d5ed3312c749c1","tid":389132,"uid":108356,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咁多字,搵咁多圖,真係辛苦哂</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n登我辛苦就幫我推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438672963c9efe6c9b78f597855cef64d603fcfc","tid":389132,"uid":34075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c42e2710be78b5461c5bd1d2a60f29d94cb637e","tid":389132,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3814c820a7fde02087e3cfe8c056b184ae1cae7c","tid":389132,"uid":38820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"🐋"},{"pid":"eaff4c8ce42f6c869567b96637c20d95b546b306","tid":389132,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n越望越覺得似小美麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c076f7d83b662fdfe7286e3278142943a8a76f","tid":389132,"uid":7673,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"哨同倒及係2樣野黎"},{"pid":"89435be3cef7943fa6acaa8b92b6634fcce63b6a","tid":389132,"uid":73344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":